summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6289 for the improvement of Harbor Ave. Southwest from Southwest Florida St. to vacated Southwest Mexico St.; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 92369, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
